{"tid":51271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對人生感到迷茫","createTime":"2016-12-23T05:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T08:26:05.000Z","uid":54547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e8cd5e821f746864c111dbe4653c4d0cede81c3","tid":51271,"uid":54547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T05:45:15.000Z","msg":"上到大學 個目標突然冇左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同女朋友感情又變淡 想分手但又講唔出 始終一齊太耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係大學又唔想去埋堆圍威喂<br />\n同屋企人平日又唔多交流 (屋企只有男）<br />\n人生突然變得好冇趣 <br />\n想令自由每日過得充實啲 有意義啲<br />\n義工 關社活動又有做 但都好似唔係自己想要既<br />\n可唔可以搵人黎打救下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b370beb740af90d53db830a9f5454d9f7b6b61cf","tid":51271,"uid":64816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:26:05.000Z","msg":"同女朋友分手可以解決所有問題<br />\n<br />\n搵新女, 有晒目標 &gt; 帶新女返屋企, 有晒交流 &gt; 做愛, 有晒意義"}]}